text: "Typical Male" is a 1986 song by Tina Turner and is the leading single from her sixth studio album Break Every Rule. It went to number 2 in the United States, Switzerland and Norway, number 33 in the United Kingdom, number 20 in Australia, number 8 in New Zealand, number 6 in Sweden and Austria, number 1 in Spain and Finland, number 11 in Canada, number 3 in Germany, number 12 in Ireland and number 14 in the Netherlands. ==References== Category:Tina Turner songs Category:1986 songs Category:Funk pop songs Category:Funk rock songs
title: Typical Male
